 who was based on his child friend  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Alice Deverill was born about 1356, in England, United Kingdom. She married John Spencer before 1378, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died about 1400, at the age of 46."},"et":{"about 1356–abt. 1400":"umbes 1356–umbes 1400","1350–1416":"1350–1416","1378–1450":"1378–1450","1356–1400":"1356–1400","before 1378":"enne 1378","1378":"1378","1400":"1400","1356":"1356","abt. 1400":"umbes 1400","about 1356":"umbes 1356","1450":"1450","1350":"1350","1416":"1416","England":"England","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, England"},"fi":{"about 1356–abt. 1400":"noin 1356–noin 1400","1350–1416":"1350–1416","1378–1450":"1378–1450","1356–1400":"1356–1400","before 1378":"ennen vuotta 1378","1378":"1378","1400":"1400","1356":"1356","abt. 1400":"noin 1400","about 1356":"noin 1356","1450":"1450","1350":"1350","1416":"1416","England":"England","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, England"},"fr":{"about 1356–abt. 1400":"environ 1356–environ 1400","1350–1416":"1350–1416","1378–1450":"1378–1450","1356–1400":"1356–1400","before 1378":"avant 1378","1378":"1378","1400":"1400","1356":"1356","abt. 1400":"environ 1400","about 1356":"environ 1356","1450":"1450","1350":"1350","1416":"1416","England":"Angleterre","Mildenhall, Suffolk, England":"Mildenhall, Suffolk, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Alice Deverill est née environ 1356, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé John Spencer avant 1378, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Elle est décédée environ 1400, à l’âge de 46 ans."},"de":{"about 1356–abt. 1400":"um 1356–um 1400","1350–1416":"1350–1416","1378–1450":"1378–1450","1356–1400":"1356–1400","before 1378":"vor 1378","1378":"1378","1400":"1400","1356":"1356","abt. 1400":"um 1400","